      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel like i'm not alone, it feels like i'm the only one anywhere. everyone's just... against me. and even if i talk to someone, the bullying is still there tomorrow. the noise is still there. there's no real escape from it. it's like i'm trapped in a room that's slowly getting smaller and smaller and there's just no way out.",
